'''2020年钻石联赛'''是由[[国际田联|国际田联]]组织的年度户外田径系列赛的第11个赛季。自2010年创立以来，[[钻石联赛|钻石联赛]]首次对赛事进行了重大修订。比赛项目数量从32个减少到24个，两站年终总决赛也缩减为一站，分站赛也将增加到15个。在中国举办的分站赛也增加到2个。减少比赛项的目的是为了方便电视台进行转播，将比赛时间压缩到标准的90分钟电视转播格式。 每个分站赛将选择11-12个钻石项目，其它的赛事将不会被转播。失去举办钻石联赛举办资格的赛事将在[[国际田联洲巡回赛|国际田联洲巡回赛]]中亮相，它将取代[[国际田联世界挑战赛|国际田联世界挑战赛]]作为田径比赛的二级赛事。 <ref>[https://www.iaaf.org/news/press-release/diamond-league-2020-season-meetings IAAF Diamond League reaches agreement on meetings for 2020 season ] {{Wayback|url=https://www.iaaf.org/news/press-release/diamond-league-2020-season-meetings |date=20191022060340 }}. IAAF (2019-10-21). Retrieved 2019-10-23.</ref>

与上一年相比，伯明翰站由于体育场馆的翻修而将比赛场地移至[[盖茨黑德|盖茨黑德]]，而尤金站将在体育馆翻修完成后返回[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]]的[[尤金|尤金]]。多哈站也将回归卡塔尔体育俱乐部，这是2010年至2018年之间卡塔尔钻石联赛的举办场地。由于[[罗马奥林匹克体育场|罗马奥林匹克体育场]]的翻新工程，罗马站的比赛将在[[那不勒斯|那不勒斯]]的[[圣保罗球场|圣保罗球场]]举行。2020赛季的最初计划是将取消斯德哥尔摩站，并将日程表缩短到更短的时间范围内，但在与中国企业集团[[万达集团|万达集团]]达成了冠名赞助协议后，这些计划被取消。<ref>[https://www.athleticsweekly.com/athletics-news/gateshead-included-in-2020-diamond-league-season-1039926187/  Gateshead included in 2020 Diamond League season] {{Wayback|url=https://www.athleticsweekly.com/athletics-news/gateshead-included-in-2020-diamond-league-season-1039926187/ |date=20201021102042 }}. ''Athletics Weekly'' (2019-10-22). Retrieved 2019-10-23.</ref><ref>[https://www.iaaf.org/news/press-release/zurich-to-host-diamond-league-final-in-2020-a Zurich to host Diamond League final in 2020 and 2021 as the League undergoes reform to become stronger and more relevant to athletes and fans] {{Wayback|url=https://www.iaaf.org/news/press-release/zurich-to-host-diamond-league-final-in-2020-a |date=20190826115230 }}. IAAF (2019-08-26). Retrieved 2019-10-23.</ref><ref>[https://www.iaaf.org/news/press-release/wanda-group-title-sponsor-for-diamond-league IAAF announces Wanda Group in landmark title sponsorship of Diamond League] {{Wayback|url=https://www.iaaf.org/news/press-release/wanda-group-title-sponsor-for-diamond-league |date=20190926220050 }}. IAAF (2019-09-25). Retrieved 2019-10-23.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-athletics-sweden-idUSKBN1W51DU |title=Athletics: Stockholm loses Diamond League status |author=O'Connor, Philip |publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |date=20 September 2019 |accessdate=20 September 2019 |archive-date=2020-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918100040/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-athletics-sweden-idUSKBN1W51DU |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

